Comment: 0,0:24:28.06,0:24:31.21,歌CN_Center_Bottom,perchar,0,0,0,kara,今天仍然喧闹的世界
Comment: 0,0:24:31.33,0:24:34.66,歌CN_Center_Bottom,perchar,0,0,0,kara,在这样半梦半醒下去就会被落下
Comment: 0,0:24:34.66,0:24:38.27,歌CN_Center_Bottom,perchar,0,0,0,kara,今天的我依旧空荡荡的
Comment: 0,0:24:38.41,0:24:41.77,歌CN_Center_Bottom,perchar,0,0,0,kara,眺望着那遥远的世界
Comment: 0,0:24:41.91,0:24:45.27,歌CN_Center_Bottom,perchar,0,0,0,kara,一呼一吸 越发窒息
Comment: 0,0:24:45.47,0:24:48.77,歌CN_Center_Bottom,perchar,0,0,0,kara,只有自己如同异类一般
Comment: 0,0:24:48.99,0:24:52.26,歌CN_Center_Bottom,perchar,0,0,0,kara,寻找着孤独的归处
Comment: 0,0:24:52.53,0:24:56.96,歌CN_Center_Bottom,perchar,0,0,0,kara,摇摇晃晃 飘向远方
Comment: 0,0:24:57.14,0:24:58.06,歌CN_Center_Bottom,perchar,0,0,0,kara,是啊
Comment: 0,0:24:58.06,0:25:00.94,歌CN_Center_Bottom,perchar,0,0,0,kara,无法飞翔的我只好游着前行
Comment: 0,0:25:00.94,0:25:04.46,歌CN_Center_Bottom,perchar,0,0,0,kara,就算我一个人会溺水的日子
Comment: 0,0:25:04.46,0:25:10.83,歌CN_Center_Bottom,perchar,0,0,0,kara,我一直渴望着拥有翅膀
Comment: 0,0:25:11.05,0:25:12.22,歌CN_Center_Bottom,perchar,0,0,0,kara,但并非如此
Comment: 0,0:25:12.22,0:25:18.82,歌CN_Center_Bottom,perchar,0,0,0,kara,就算双脚失去知觉 在那隐隐作痛的海底
Comment: 0,0:25:18.82,0:25:24.66,歌CN_Center_Bottom,perchar,0,0,0,kara,但此刻的我 仍然在呼吸
Comment: 0,0:25:25.83,0:25:29.23,歌CN_Center_Bottom,perchar,0,0,0,kara,Ah Ah
Comment: 0,0:25:29.38,0:25:33.47,歌CN_Center_Bottom,perchar,0,0,0,kara,Ah Ah
Comment: 0,0:24:28.06,0:24:31.21,歌JP_Center_Bottom,perchar,0,0,0,kara,周りは今日も騒がしい
Comment: 0,0:24:31.33,0:24:34.66,歌JP_Center_Bottom,perchar,0,0,0,kara,寝ぼけたままじゃ置いてかれる
Comment: 0,0:24:34.66,0:24:38.27,歌JP_Center_Bottom,perchar,0,0,0,kara,今僕は空虚なままで
Comment: 0,0:24:38.41,0:24:41.77,歌JP_Center_Bottom,perchar,0,0,0,kara,遠くの世界を見ている
Comment: 0,0:24:41.91,0:24:45.27,歌JP_Center_Bottom,perchar,0,0,0,kara,吸って吐いて苦しくなって
Comment: 0,0:24:45.47,0:24:48.77,歌JP_Center_Bottom,perchar,0,0,0,kara,自分だけが異物みたいだ
Comment: 0,0:24:48.99,0:24:52.26,歌JP_Center_Bottom,perchar,0,0,0,kara,孤独の居場所探しながら
Comment: 0,0:24:52.53,0:24:56.96,歌JP_Center_Bottom,perchar,0,0,0,kara,ゆらりゆれるどこまでも
Comment: 0,0:24:57.14,0:24:58.06,歌JP_Center_Bottom,perchar,0,0,0,kara,そうさ
Comment: 0,0:24:58.06,0:25:00.94,歌JP_Center_Bottom,perchar,0,0,0,kara,飛べない僕は泳いだ
Comment: 0,0:25:00.94,0:25:04.46,歌JP_Center_Bottom,perchar,0,0,0,kara,一人溺れそうになる日でも
Comment: 0,0:25:04.46,0:25:10.83,歌JP_Center_Bottom,perchar,0,0,0,kara,ずっと羽を欲しがっていたけれど けれど
Comment: 0,0:25:11.05,0:25:12.22,歌JP_Center_Bottom,perchar,0,0,0,kara,違うんだ
Comment: 0,0:25:12.22,0:25:18.82,歌JP_Center_Bottom,perchar,0,0,0,kara,足もおぼつかないまま 渦いている深い海の底で
Comment: 0,0:25:18.82,0:25:24.66,歌JP_Center_Bottom,perchar,0,0,0,kara,僕は今 息をしてる
Comment: 0,0:25:25.83,0:25:29.23,歌JP_Center_Bottom,perchar,0,0,0,kara,あー あー
Comment: 0,0:25:29.38,0:25:33.47,歌JP_Center_Bottom,perchar,0,0,0,kara,あー あー
